Global Electrically Switched Permanent Lifting Magnet Market Insights
Electrically Switched Permanent Lifting Magnet Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Electrically Switched Permanent Lifting Magnet Market Overview
The Electrically Switched Permanent Lifting Magnet market is expected to reach a value of USD 3.2 billion by 2030, growing at a steady CAGR of 7.8% from 2023 to 2030. The increasing demand for automation and lifting solutions in industries like manufacturing, steel, and construction is driving the market's growth. The ability of electrically switched permanent magnets to offer reliable, safe, and energy-efficient solutions for material handling is further fueling their adoption across various sectors. The demand for these magnets is anticipated to rise as industries seek sustainable and cost-effective alternatives to traditional lifting technologies.

